  (str hindiTitle) (str `औद्योगिक विकास बैंक (उपक्रम का अंतरण और निरसन) अधिनियम,2003`)
  (str actYear) (str 2003)
  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Finance`)
  (str department) (str `Department of Financial Services`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the transfer and vesting of the undertaking of the Industrial Development Bank of India to, and in, the Company to be formed and registered as a Company under the Companies Act, 1956 to carry on banking business and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto and also to repeal the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964.`)
